LABOTS
======

IRC bot framework written in python 3.x, just works for myself.


Features
--------

* Run multiple bots with single IRC bot
* Useful IRC bot interface
* Dynamic {load,unload} bots (Pyinotify)
* Asynchronous socket and IO (Tornado)


Requires
--------

* Python 3
* Pyinotify 0.9.4
* Tornado 3.2.2


Usage
-----

Please see `bots/example.py` or https://github.com/lastavenger/labots


Bots
----

See <https://github.com/LastAvenger/bots>.


References
----------

* https://github.com/lilydjwg/archrepo2
* https://github.com/nod/iobot
* https://github.com/LukeusMaximus/Python-IRC-Bot-Framework


